changelog:
0.1.6
Update to a more user friendly interaction behavior, courtesy of @ZHDreamer
Any unit of time can now easily be "left and right" navigated to and changed at ease
Streamline build and release with GH Actions, initiated by @gzk47
Builds can now be obtained more easily and will run on a commit-by-commit basis on GitHub
Built with latest toolchain versions for HOS 21+ ABI support
General software stability improvements to enhance the user's experience
Credits:

@thedax for NX-ntpc, from which the parent project is forked.
@Cytraen for changing the servers to cloudfare.
@vonhabsbourg for adding month and year change.
@izenn for the watch icon created by Freepik - Flaticon.
@ZHDreamer for adding left-right navigable interaction.
@gzk47 for starting the GH Actions CI for this project.
